cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.controllers

Class PostController

  • java.lang.Object
    • cs.ualberta.CMPUT301F14T08.stackunderflow.controllers.PostController

  • public class PostController
extends java.lang.Object
    StackUnderflow application PostController. Point of access for post manager - handles differences between online/cached post manager automatically. Determines whether to provide online or cache manager based on online/offline status.
    Author:
    Cmput301 Winter 2014 Group 8
